Hi Everyone,
I am sending out this invite to my Seraph  group, we have been on yahoo 
since Oct. of 98!  There is plenty of storage  room where you may create 
folders and posting for EVP files, it's a quiet group,  but maybe your people will 
get our group talking a bit more.  We are  called, "Seraph, the highest 
order of angels."  Here is the link  below,
Tks. sf
